frames.caption: A DeLorean car, reminiscent of a time machine, is parked in a muddy, overgrown area in front of an iconic Russian cathedral with colorful onion domes. The scene suggests a juxtaposition of futuristic technology and historical architecture, set against a backdrop of decay and neglect.
frames.description: The scene depicts a DeLorean car situated in a muddy, overgrown landscape, with the iconic Saint Basil's Cathedral in the background. This setting combines elements of futuristic technology with historical architecture, creating a surreal atmosphere.

frames.caption: A weathered car is partially submerged in a muddy, overgrown area in front of a historic, ornate building with colorful domes. The scene suggests a post-apocalyptic setting with nature reclaiming the area. The building's architecture is reminiscent of Eastern European styles, adding a sense of historical significance to the desolate environment.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dystopian landscape where a classic car is stuck in mud, surrounded by overgrown vegetation. In the background, a grand, colorful domed building stands, partially obscured by mist and decay. The setting suggests abandonment and the passage of time, with nature overtaking human-made structures.
